My Boss Rocky Santuari was created/rendered by Thobie Buntaran a.k.a. Loreng on 30 June 2021, Mantrijeron, Yogyakarta, Indonesia.

I took this pic when I was visiting their SMS (Santuari Mobile Studio) in Yogyakarta.
They appeared to be looking for a sign from the Crystal Matahari location In the region.
At that time, Rocky told me about some ancient celestials who possessed the crystal Matahari energy.
I remember they mentioned about something fast, high speed, full of energy is coming soon and will wreak havoc in the entire realms.
